<p><q>He had a <qex>feck</qex> o' books wi' him.</q> <rj><qau>R. L.
Stevenson.</qau></rj></p>

<p><cs><mcol><col><b>The most feck</b></col>, <it>or</it> <col><b>The
feck</b></col></mcol>, <cd>the greater or larger part.</cd> ⟦ldquo⟧The
<xex>feck</xex> o' my life.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>Burns.</au></cs>⟦br⟧
